outputs.output_descr:
Development and implementation of TOKTEN's advocacy and outreach strategy
Identification of beneficiary institutions and available skills to arrange, monitor, and evaluate TOKTEN missions

project_descr: This project aims at reinforcing Government efforts to strengthen technical capacities in key sectors and institutions and establish a mechanism whereby the country can tap into the skills base of its expatriate nationals.
project_title: Transfer of Knowledge Through Expatriate Nationals
